"Show line numbers
set number

"Mouse Config
set mouse=a

"Search Options
set hlsearch
set incsearch

"Syntax Highlight
filetype plugin on
syntax on

"With this option the search next behaviour allows to jump to the beginning of
"the file, when the end of file is reached. Similarly, search previous jumps
"to the end of the file when the start is reached.
set wrapscan
